Petition of prestigious universities in Iași and country
More than 200 researchers, academics, personalities and students from the country have signed a petition launched by the Academic Society of Romania in which they ask the Ministry of Education and Scientific Research to evaluate, sanction and even abolish doctoral schools in Romania "that allow and promote academic deception".
Among the signatories of the petition launched on September 10 are teachers and teachers from Iași.
